==== 盛行狀況 ====
在[[維吉尼亞理工學院暨州立大學|維吉尼亞理工學院暨州立大學]]2006年發佈的一項研究中指出，在受歡迎遊戲的評論裡、與可玩的女性角色有關的評論出現在討論裡的頻率低於男性角色。<ref>Ivory, J. D. (2006). [http://filebox.vt.edu/users/jivory/JIvory2006MassCommunicationandSociety.pdf Still a man's game: Gender representation in online reviews of video games.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224015022/http://filebox.vt.edu/users/jivory/JIvory2006MassCommunicationandSociety.pdf |date=2014-12-24 }} Mass Communication & Society, 9(1), 103-114. The sample of reviews was taken from the "Top Rated" and "Most Popular" lists from [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] on March 26, 2004.</ref><ref>Miller, M. K., & Summers, A. (2007). [http://www.easternct.edu/~lugow/courses/videogames/gender_videogames.pdf Gender differences in video game characters' roles, appearances, and attire as portrayed in video game magazines.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101083815/http://www.easternct.edu/~lugow/courses/videogames/gender_videogames.pdf |date=2015-01-01 }} Sex roles, 57(9-10), 733-742.</ref>2007年，由Melinda C. R. Burgess等人所做的研究中發現，男性角色出現在[[電子遊樂器|電子遊樂器]]遊戲封面上的次數要高於女性角色。<ref name=Burgess>{{cite journal|last=Burgess|first=Melinda C. R. |author2=Steven Paul Stermer |author3=Stephen R. Burgess|title=Sex, Lies, and Video Games: The Portrayal of Male and Female Characters on Video Game Covers|journal=Sex Roles|date=30 June 2007|pages=419–433|doi=10.1007/s11199-007-9250-0|volume=57|issue=5–6}}</ref>

2012年，{{link-en|電子娛樂設計與研究|Electronic Entertainment Design and Research}}抽樣了包括動作、射擊、角色扮演遊戲等669款遊戲後發現，其中有300款（45%）的遊戲能讓玩家選擇女性做為主角，相較於2010年的10%高出許多。<ref name="escapistEEDAR"/>

2015年刊載於《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》上、由Madeline Messer撰寫的文章中表示：前50個受歡迎的無盡奔跑類手機遊戲中，可選性別的遊戲裡有98%提供男性主角，而其中90%是免費遊戲。只有46%的遊戲提供女性主角，而其中15%是免費遊戲。身為女孩、平均要花費額外的7.53美元才能玩到和自己同樣性別的角色，而這個金額甚至超過遊戲本身的售價。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Messer|first1=Madeline|title=I’m a 12-year-old girl. Why don’t the characters in my apps look like me?|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/posteverything/wp/2015/03/04/im-a-12-year-old-girl-why-dont-the-characters-in-my-apps-look-like-me/|accessdate=12 April 2015|date=4 March 2015}}</ref>

==== 演變 ====
《[[銀河戰士系列|銀河戰士]]》系列在1986年推出的第一作《[[銀河戰士_(遊戲)|銀河戰士]]》的女英雄[[薩姆斯·阿蘭|薩姆斯·阿蘭]]經常被視為「主流電子遊戲中首位人類女性可玩角色」<ref name="Guinness2013">{{cite book | title=Guinness World Records 2013: Gamer's Edition | url=https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec0000unse_k6v8 | publisher=Guinness World Records Ltd | authorlink=Feature: Girl Power-Up | year=2012 | page=[https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec0000unse_k6v8/page/154 154] | isbn=9781904994954}}</ref>，不過也是有其它更早的女性可玩角色，例如[[南夢宮|南夢宮]]在1985年推出的射擊遊戲《{{link-en|バラデューク|バラデューク}}》的角色{{lang|ja|トビ・マスヨ}}。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/namcoxcapcom/namcoxcapcom2.htm#tobymasuyo | title=Obscure Namco characters | publisher=Hardcore Gaming 101 | accessdate=6 October 2013 | author=Kurt Kalata | archive-date=2013-09-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130926182846/http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/namcoxcapcom/namcoxcapcom2.htm#tobymasuyo | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2009/10/nintendo_download_13_14_october_2009_japan | title=Nintendo Download: 13-14 October 2009 (Japan) | publisher=nintendolife.com | accessdate=6 October 2013 | author=Sean Aaron | archive-date=2013-10-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006174808/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2009/10/nintendo_download_13_14_october_2009_japan | dead-url=no }}</ref>

早在1970年代便有社會學、教育和文化期刊開始研究女性角色在電子遊戲裡的普遍性。1979年的《心理記錄》（Psychological Record Vol.29, No.1. 43–48頁）從在訪問了201人後得出結論，90%的男性受試者和85%的女性受試者將電腦視為[[男性氣質|男性氣質]]的（電腦包括電子遊戲）<ref name=leroux>Leroux, Yvan and Michel Pépin. "Jeu Sur Micro-Ordinateur et Différences Liées au Sexe". ''Revue des Sciences de l'Education''. Vol.XII, No.2. Pp.173-196. 1986. {{ISSN|0318-479X}}</ref> ；1983年，{{link-en|沙拉·基斯勒|Sara Kiesler}}教授等人在《{{link-en|今日心理學|Psychology Today}}》(Vol.17, No.3. 40–48頁.) 上刊載一項研究，發現電子遊戲裡有女性角色的頻率是七分之一<ref name=leroux/> ，Elizabeth Behm-Morawitz認為女性角色之所以罕見、是因為它們在遊戲裡扮演的角色並不重要。當一位女性的可玩角色出現在電子遊戲中時、它們相較於男性角色經常是更暴露、更性化的。<ref>Behm-Morawitz, Elizabeth, and Dana Mastro. "The Effects of the Sexualization of Female Video Game Characters on Gender Stereotyping and Female Self-Concept." Sex Roles 61.11 (2009): 808-823. ProQuest. Web. 22 April 2014.</ref>

《[[古墓奇兵系列|古墓奇兵]]》系列的主角[[蘿拉·卡芙特|蘿拉·卡芙特]]是非常著名的、強悍的虛構女性角色之一<ref name="taylor">{{cite book | last1 = Egenfeldt-Nielsen | first1 = Simon | last2 = Smith | first2 = Jonas Heide | last3 = Pajares Tosca | first3 = Susana | title = Understanding video games: the essential introduction | chapter = Player culture | publisher = Taylor & Francis | year = 2008 | page = 163 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=31XHdVXlbt0C&lpg=PP1&dq=%22april%20ryan%22&pg=PA163#v=onepage&q=%22april%20ryan%22&f=false | accessdate = 2011-07-03 | isbn = 978-0-415-97721-0 | quote = "Helen Kennedy [...] summarizes these arguments, and Lara Croft's ambivalent role as both an action heroine [...], and an eroticized object of the male gaze with a great deal of voyeuristic appeal".}}</ref>。在她於1996年於《[[古墓奇兵_(1996年遊戲)|古墓奇兵]]》初次登場時，她那對不合常理的巨大乳房受到不少批評；她被稱為「一位在性別、性慾、賦權和物化上引發文化衝突的現在進行式」<ref name="gettingthegirl">{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3137700 |author=Zoe Flower |title=Getting the Girl: The myths, misconceptions, and misdemeanors of females in games |publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |accessdate=2007-09-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071218083755/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3137700 |archivedate=2007-12-18 }}</ref>。在2008年的《古墓奇兵》裡、蘿拉身穿[[露臍上衣|露臍上衣]]和[[熱褲|熱褲]]，她的這個造型被評為「是由男人為她裝扮的」<ref>{{cite web|title=Tomb Raider Lara Croft now Battling Video Game Sterotypes|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/games/tomb-raider-lara-croft-now-battling-video-game-stereotypes/#/0|website=Hero Comles|accessdate=2017-01-20|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203063950/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/games/tomb-raider-lara-croft-now-battling-video-game-stereotypes/#/0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過遊戲的設計者卻聲稱，蘿拉的設計與市場取向無關，並表示對她受到海報女郎式的崇拜感到驚訝<ref>{{cite news |title=Lara Croft, the Bit Girl |author=N'gai Croal and Jane Hughes |publisher=[[Newsweek|Newsweek]] |date=1997-11-10}}</ref>。在《[[古墓奇兵：不死傳奇|古墓奇兵：不死傳奇]]》裡，蘿拉的設計改頭換面，讓她的形象少了許多性感元素。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lara's curves reduced to appeal to female gamers |date=2005-05-21 |publisher=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] |url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/World/Real-appeal/2005/05/21/1116533572111.html |accessdate=2007-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071015084057/http://www.smh.com.au/news/World/Real-appeal/2005/05/21/1116533572111.html |archivedate=October 15, 2007 }}</ref>

《[[無盡的旅程|無盡的旅程]]》（1999）的女英雄{{link-en|四月天|April Ryan (The Longest Journey)}}經常被拿來與蘿拉·卡芙特比較。相較於蘿拉的男性化與侵略性，四月天的外表較沒有性感的元素、但性格上更女性化<ref name="merete">{{cite web | url = http://www.csi.ensmp.fr/WebCSI/4S/download/download_page.php?file=lie.pdf | title = Lara Croft and her sisters | accessdate = 2011-07-03 | last = Lie | first = Merete | publisher = Norwegian University of Science and Technology | quote = "She is attractive, but no sex bomb"  "April may, however, appear as more feminine because even if she is tough and brave, she is depicted as both sensitive and vain" | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110929140119/http://www.csi.ensmp.fr/WebCSI/4S/download/download_page.php?file=lie.pdf | archivedate = 2011-09-29 }}</ref> 。《[[神鬼冒險|神鬼冒險]]》（2003）的女英雄{{link-en|翠玉|Jade (Beyond Good & Evil)}}被公認為是個強大、有自信、也沒有任何顯著性化的女性。<ref>{{cite web|last=Rougeau|first=Michael|url=http://www.complex.com/video-games/2013/01/the-50-greatest-heroines-in-video-game-history/jade|title=50 Greatest Heroines In Video Game History|publisher=Complex|date=March 4, 2013|accessdate=March 24, 2013|archive-date=2013-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130307091140/http://www.complex.com/video-games/2013/01/the-50-greatest-heroines-in-video-game-history/jade|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Bayonetta: empowering or exploitative?|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/213466/bayonetta-empowering-or-exploitative/ |publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]] |accessdate=2010-01-16|date=2010-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100109032922/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/213466/bayonetta-empowering-or-exploitative/|archivedate=2010-01-09}}</ref>

2014年時，由於《[[極地戰嚎系列|極地戰嚎]]》和《[[刺客教條|刺客教條]]》的開發人員選擇在最新的系列作遊戲中將女性可玩角色刪除，因而成為遊戲界討論的焦點。根據[[Polygon|Polygon]]引自遊戲業界專家的評論指出，遊戲業的目光從過去以年輕男性為主的市場移往電子遊戲的多樣性問題，這會使電子遊戲獲得整體性的提升。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Crecente|first1=Brian|title=As game players diversify, developers start to rethink the stars of their games|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/6/23/5834628/women-in-video-games-heroines-e3-2014|accessdate=23 June 2014|work=Polygon|date=23 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625082304/http://www.polygon.com/2014/6/23/5834628/women-in-video-games-heroines-e3-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>

